Speaker 1: Okay. So you're getting the AGB 100 milligrams.

Speaker 2: Okay. So you want to order how many did you want to go with?

Speaker 1: You want it to be 10 again as last time or what?

Speaker 2: What kind of deals you got?

Speaker 2: It will be the same price you're paying for the 40.

Speaker 1: For the tax, it will be $163.95.

Speaker 2: And then the 25 pills for $99.

Speaker 1: And then the 10 pills was for the $49.

Speaker 2: So I might as well get the 40, right, the cheaper?

Speaker 1: Yeah. The more you get, the cheaper they are.

Speaker 2: That is correct.

Speaker 1: They ain't got no kind of pills you take, like, every day,

Speaker 2: and it just works when you need it?

Speaker 1: They ain't got nothing like that?

Speaker 2: Well, the Viagra is the best pill that's out there right now.

Speaker 1: The new one that we sent you, the AGB, I mean, like you say, it does work better.

Speaker 2: And you're getting the 100 milligrams.

Speaker 1: So there's not too much that's out there better than the one that you're taking.

Speaker 2: Okay. That's what I know.

Speaker 1: Okay, then.

Speaker 2: The other ones I was getting, I called and complained because they weren't even working.

Speaker 1: Right.

Speaker 2: But they sent you the new and improved ones, and I'm sure, like you mentioned,

Speaker 1: those are the ones that's the best on the market right now.

Speaker 2: Yeah, they are working better.

Speaker 1: You are right.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: So you want to go with 40 of those?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: And I don't want to be on a plan I call when I need something.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: The best I can do, I can push it out for, like, about five or six months.

Speaker 1: Because in order to get these, you do have to keep your prescription on file.

Speaker 2: And that's what they did for you last time.

Speaker 1: Oh, you do?

Speaker 2: Yeah, they kept the prescription on file.

Speaker 1: Okay, I got you.

Speaker 2: So that's what they did.

Speaker 1: Go ahead.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: And then if I need them before the five months, I can call you, right?

Speaker 2: You can call.

Speaker 1: That's exactly correct.

Speaker 2: Do it that way, sir.

Speaker 1: That's exactly correct.

Speaker 2: Okay, not a problem.

Speaker 1: Yeah, do the five months, yeah.

Speaker 2: That'll work.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Okay, sounds good.

Speaker 2: Okay, I just took care of that for you.

Speaker 1: And I went ahead and updated your account.

Speaker 2: So it's going to be every five months.

Speaker 1: And you can call any time before then to order.

Speaker 2: And it should take about five to seven business days to get there.

Speaker 1: It should come sooner.

Speaker 2: But that's the average time that it takes.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Well, what is it?

Speaker 1: Just a new manufacturer or something?

Speaker 2: Is that what's going on?

Speaker 1: Well, it's the same manufacturer.

Speaker 2: I'm from FireSafe Labs in France.

Speaker 1: But they just decided to just improve it.

Speaker 2: You know how things get improved, you know, with technology.

Speaker 1: So the technology just got better.

Speaker 2: And the new and improved Viagra, it works faster.

Speaker 1: It lasts longer.

Speaker 2: And it doesn't have those same side effects that people would get,

Speaker 1: like the dizziness and headaches and the stomach aches.

Speaker 2: Oh, yeah.

Speaker 1: You know, you breathe more and all that.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I don't get all that.

Speaker 1: Exactly.

Speaker 2: Exactly.

Speaker 1: So that's the improvement.

Speaker 2: You're right.

Speaker 1: Okay, so that's why they're the new and improved.

Speaker 2: Same company that made the original Viagra,

Speaker 1: they just improved the quality of these pills.

Speaker 2: That's what these are.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay?

Speaker 1: All right?

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: Have a good day.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
